# A condition where a person, especially a child, has difficulty with bonding to others
# A condition where a person, especially a child, is incapable of bonding with other
# A condition where a person, especially a child, is incapable of bonding with others to normal levels of bonding, social interaction, and affection.

==== Notes =====
# Often found in autistic children
# Often found in abused children
# Often found in children from alcoholic homes
# Often found in children from multiple foster homes/living situations
# If left untreated, can grow into antisocial personality disorder